properties.Name: PersonalLineOfCreditSummary
properties.Description: A variable interest rate line of credit that requires collateral or security.

Columns.Name: CreditGrantorId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Credit Grantor.

Columns.Name: LoanAccountNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a loan.

Columns.Name: MaximumLineOfCreditAmount
Columns.Description: The maximum amount of line of credit that may be extended.

Columns.Name: MinimumPaymentAmount
Columns.Description: The minimum amount that must be paid upon the line of credit each payment period.

Columns.Name: MinimumPaymentPercentageOfBalance
Columns.Description:
The minimum payment per payment period expressed as a percentage of the total incurred.

Ex:
$25 or 1/120th of outstanding principal, whichever is greater, plus accrued interest.

Columns.Name: PersonalLineOfCreditNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the personal line of credit.

Columns.Name: InterestRateIndexId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Interest Rate Index.

Columns.Name: ChecksIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether loan draft checks are available for this specific line of credit issued.

Columns.Name: AutomaticPaymentIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether automatic payment are available for this specific line of credit issued.

Columns.Name: MonthlyStatementsIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether monthly statements are available for this specific line of credit issued.

Columns.Name: CashAdvancesIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether cash advances are available for this specific line of credit issued.

Columns.Name: CreditChecksIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether credit checks are available for this specific line of credit issued.

Columns.Name: AtmAccessIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether ATM access to the line of credit funds is provided.

Columns.Name: 24HourInternetAccessIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether 24 hour internet access to account information is available for this specific line of credit issued.

Columns.Name: 24HourTelephoneAccessIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether 24 hour telephone access to account information is available for this specific line of credit issued.

Properties.Description: A variable interest rate line of credit that requires collateral or security.
